# Kabianga University Examiner System (KUES)

## AI Detection, Marks and Report Management for Take-Away and Assignment CATs

### Project Overview

The Kabianga University Examiner System (KUES) is a Flask-based web application developed to assist lecturers and examiners in analyzing student submissions for possible AI-generated content. The system combines Optical Character Recognition (OCR), Machine Learning, and explainable AI techniques to evaluate student assignments, CATs, and take-away examinations.

The system supports both typed and handwritten documents and provides detailed AI probability reports together with marks and record management functionality.

