## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/heeds2002/KUES.git
```

### Navigate to Project

```bash
cd KUES
```

### Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

### Activate Environment

Windows:

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run Application

```bash
python app.py
```

### Open Browser

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

